name: Firebrick
tagline: A powerful JavaScript Framework powered by jQuery, Bootstrap, Knockout JS and Require JS
body:
#Firebrick JS

[http://www.firebrickjs.com](http://www.firebrickjs.com)

JavaScript MVC Framework built with:

* jQuery
* Bootstrap
* Knockout JS
* Require JS

## Install with Bower
```
bower install firebrick
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
